{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idedd1f739-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"9c"},"text":"§ 9c.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Notice of investigations and enforcement actions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Commission shall provide the Securities and Exchange Commission with notice of the commencement of any proceeding and a copy of any order entered by the Commission pursuant to section 9 and 13b of this title against any futures commission merchant or introducing broker registered pursuant to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s6f/a/2"},"text":"section 6f(a)(2) of this title","children":[],"tail":", any floor broker or floor trader exempt from registration pursuant to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s6f/a/3"},"text":"section 6f(a)(3) of this title","children":[],"tail":", any associated person exempt from registration pursuant to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s6k/6"},"text":"section 6k(6) of this title","children":[],"tail":", or any board of trade designated as a contract market pursuant to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s7b–1"},"text":"section 7b–1 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idedd1f73a-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1922-09-21/ch369/s6/g"},"text":"Sept. 21, 1922, ch. 369, § 6(g)","children":[],"tail":", as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/554/s1/a/5/tII/s253/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–554, § 1(a)(5) [title II, § 253(b)]","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2000-12-21"},"text":"Dec. 21, 2000","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/114/2763"},"text":"114 Stat. 2763","children":[],"tail":", 2763A–449.)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idedd1f73b-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idedd1f73c-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"idedd1f73d-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section is comprised of subsec. (g) of section 6 of act ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1922-09-21"},"text":"Sept. 21, 1922","children":[],"tail":". Subsecs. (a) and (b) of section 6 are classified to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s8"},"text":"section 8 of this title","children":[],"tail":". Subsec. (c) of section 6 is classified to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s9"},"text":"section 9 of this title","children":[],"tail":". Subsecs. (d), (e), and (f) of section 6 are classified to sections 13b, 9a, and 9b of this title, respectively."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
